Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[birds chirping]\N-[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Hilda ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolling in distance]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell continues tolling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs calling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[caws]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] See that, Twig?\NIt's a troll rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Trolls don't usually come this far\Ndown the mountain. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to draw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure that's a nose,\Nand those must be arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[snorts, growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't worry, boy.\N-[whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This troll can't even think\Nabout eating us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there's daylight,\Nit's just a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, once the sun goes down,\Nwe're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you hang this on its nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If the troll moves, the bell jingles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll know it's time\Nto run for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Done! I think I'm happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... maybe one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[crackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And, there.\NThat's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bell jingles]\N-[crackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[woffs grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we had that bell.\NI think we outran him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[sniffing]\N-[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-[snorts]\N-What is it, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's a huge footprint,\Neven for a forest giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell jingles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-[footsteps approaching]\N-[bell jingling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[insects chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost him in the woods, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell jingles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts]\N-[bell jingling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Twig, I think he's in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell's driving him crazy, poor thing.\NAnd his arms, they're too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling, whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Mr. Troll. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts, screams]\N-[roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! My sketchbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was pretty traumatic,\Nbut such is the life of an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-[glassware clinking]\N-[Mum] Hilda, I've made us some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am seriously appreciating\Nthe coziness in here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-[blows, slurps]\N-[man whistling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[whistling tune]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mum scoffs] The Wood Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[whistling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mum] He always just comes in\Nwithout knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] It's okay.\NHe probably just wants to get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, he brings us wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] It's drafty in here.\NYou should really close that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-[knocking on door]\N-[sighs] Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[owl hooting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another one of those tiny letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief,\Nthis is the sixth one this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it from the hidden people again?\N-Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they still saying we have to move\Nand they're gonna smash our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Basically.\N-Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're tiny\Nand they don't like us very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear to whom it may concern,\Nplease leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are nice people,\Nso please stop being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All the best, Hilda."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, little guys,\Nwhoever you are, this one's for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wood Man] I can't read\Nwith all these distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe your note will do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish our game of Dragon Panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it my turn next or yours?\N-Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[insects chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-[man on TV grunting]\N-[Mum and Hilda snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps pattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[static crackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[male voice] Attention, residents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to your failure to heed our warnings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall now implement\Nyour forcible eviction from the premises!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forcible eviction now!\NBanish the big boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ow! Ow! Mum!\N-Hilda... [shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Mum! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[male voice] Jettison the giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[male voices] Heave ho, you must go!\NHeave ho, you must go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's enough.\N-[male voices yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[male voices chattering] Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get out!\N-[male voice] Stop! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-[grunts]\N-They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mum, they're--\N-[glass crunches]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, we can't stay here,\Nnot if this is gonna keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-We've never been attacked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll have to move to Trolberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've been here for all time,\Nsince I was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving to Trolberg could be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You could make some proper friends.\NWouldn't that be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I love it here in the wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's literally the best place ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Please, Mum, I don't want\Nto live in the dirty old city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but if one more thing\Nlike this happens, we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear little guys who trashed my house,\Nwhy are you so mad at me and my mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me so I can fix it\Nand we can all live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All the best, Hilda."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they're not too mad\Nto even read my note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to bed and get some rest, eh?\NWe'll clean all this up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps pattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Alfur] Psst! Little girl!\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur] I'm one of the little people\Nwho trashed your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The trashing\Nwasn't done by me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more of a writer than a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you read my note?\N-Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're\Njust a voice inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why won't you show yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my people take the business of who\Nsees them and who doesn't very seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which means, of course,\Nthat there's a lot of paperwork involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll just go over to your desk,\Nplease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the liberty of filling out\Nthe relevant papers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find the forgery\Nquite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda] Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll sign this last page\Nyourself, we'll be all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This better not be some kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Now, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat] Look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't--\N-Your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Coo-ee! [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very, very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, I'm on the tall side for an elf,\Nactually, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Alfur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's nice to finally see you, Alfur.\N-It's nice to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll come outside with me,\Nthere's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[snarles]\N-[electricity crackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful there, Twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have these been here all the time,\Nand I just couldn't see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-[screaming]\N-Somebody lives there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whoops.\N-[Alfur] Yeah, whoops, indeed. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Behavior like that\Nwill not endear you to elfkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Sorry about that.\N-[huffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How many houses are there?\NHow far does this go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur] I dare say\Nas far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's 15 counties in this valley alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and your house is smack\Nin the middle of my one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But why get mad now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My great-granddad built that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived here all my life,\Nand there hasn't been any bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] It's the new prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised to get rid of you\Nif he was elected, and... [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...now that he has been,\Nhe has to see to it that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not fair! We're allowed\Nto live here as much as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers] Don't shout at me!\NI agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, if you weren't so sniffy\Nabout who sees you and who doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe my granddad would've chosen\Nsomewhere a bit less populated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important tradition of my people\Nto be sniffy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So take me to the prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could\Nexplain things to him and fix this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,before Mum moves us to Trolberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing,\Nit's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And, for another, you can't simply request\Na meeting to go and say, "Hello!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-But I'm the giant girl, so--\N-The mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll arrange a meeting\Nwith the mayor of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,your house is currently occupying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he can help us\Nwith the prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, okay, but--\N-Got to dash now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come for you tomorrow.\NGood night, Hilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hilda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Twig whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum is not going to like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur] Remember, allow me\Nto handle the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[fanfare playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Honorable Mayor,\Nmay I have the pleasure of--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know who you are.\NThe giant, the menace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so, you can see us, can you?\NFinally noticed us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-[mocking] Ooh.\N-Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I notice you\Nif I couldn't see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, the forms\Nare very straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And where was I supposed\Nto get these forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[sputters] The forms are widely available.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing is that all the forms\Nhave now been filed, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had enough\Nof her ruthless occupation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of our historic city,\Nhaven't we, Angelina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have, haven't we?\NMeow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing ruthless about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know\Nyou even existed until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Pure ignorance!\N-You're invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[meowing]\N-Please, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,can you lower your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alarming my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look, I'm sorry about that,\Nbut, please, don't evict us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Angelina's heavily pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her unnecessarily stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a purebred velourian silkhair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fetch Angelina's basket, will you?\N-Right away, Mr. Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Do you need to lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You look the way I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not answering my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you still here?\NLook, well, wheels are in motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,plans are in place,\Nletters are being sent,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and forms are being filled in,\Nlots of forms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely you can stop it.\NYou're the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I'm only the mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't even have hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So whose hands is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I imagine the only person\Nwho could do anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is the new prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his big idea, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where can I find him?\N-I can't tell you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's classified information.\N-Tell me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, I--\N-[meowing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps] Oh, Angelina!\N-Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Release her this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the prime minister is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'll let your kitty live\Nin my hair forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you fiend! You monster!\NYou beast! Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind the waterfall, the great big one\Nthat goes into the fjord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, thank goodness!\N-The basket, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there, Angelina. There.\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going straight\Nto the prime minister this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, wait! [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that barging in like this\Ncould be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to fix this right now, Alfur,\Nand I don't need a formal introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Let's go-- [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof! [exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! A rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you took a tumble,\Npoor little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-[squeaking]\N-Ah! It's not just a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-It's the prime minister's cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Implement giant girl defense maneuvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[elf commander] Charge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[thuds, squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Implement hasty retreat maneuver!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away! Run away!\NFaster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's gaining on us! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Thanks for that, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Alfur] It's nice to have a deer fox\Non your side, I must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[drum roll]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our training is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to launch\Nour next attack this evening, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Hold on a second!\N-[elves screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I mean you no harm!\NI just want to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming stops]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, in that case,\Neverybody be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find a way\Nwe can all live together in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my home,\Nand I don't want to leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's, uh, interesting.\NLook, I'll be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only said I'd get rid of you\Nbecause I knew I'd get elected if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hip, hip!\N-Hear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really all hate\Nmy mum and me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-[elf 1] Yes!\N-[elf 2] Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You must understand\Nthat the lights from your house
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are much too bright at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For the record,\NI don't hate you even a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoyance, sometimes, yes,\Nbut never, never hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very loud.\NYou keep babies up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're always stepping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know stepping on you doesn't\Nhurt you if you haven't signed the forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Twig's leg go right through a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's a traumatic experience having\Na giant foot come through your ceilings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-[chuckles]\N-Okay, I get it, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, we can turn off our lights earlier\Nand keep our voices down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we get my mum to sign the forms,\Nthen everything should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not quite as simple as that.\N-It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your house, you and your family,\Nsince anyone can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,have been considered\Nsworn enemies of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Sworn enemies of the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever bothered to try\Nand do anything about it until me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid to say that fixing\Nthe situation at this point is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Hilda] Out of your hands?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't even have hands!\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilda, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffling, crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-[sniffles]\N-Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alfur, if I was to ask you to tell me\Nwhere the king lives, would you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it out of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] That would violate every protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffles] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, but it's a tough journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can leave\Nthe day after tomorrow at sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you, Alfur.\N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually closer to home\Nthan you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
